title.narrative: Stronger mechanisms to prevent VAWG are established at national and sub-national level (Related SP outputs 11, 12)

description.narrative: Through this outcome, UN Women Indonesia aims to contribute to the creation of environment that are free from violence against women and girls, which occure both at domestic and public spaces, including in urban setting. UN Women Indonesia also aims to realize a safe and fair migration for women migrant workers. Under this outcome, the office works closely with national and sub-national partners to review and improve the implementation of policies on ending violence against women, migrant protection and trafficking, and to increase the capacity of key stakeholders in providing coordinated quality services to victims of violence and trafficking.
